；致重傷者，處三年以上十年以下\r\n有期徒刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PTDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c615%2c20220502%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PTDM,111,交簡,615,20220502,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"615","JDATE":"20220502","JTITLE":"公共危險"}